        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Gaedren makes a Hand Crossbow Strike against Gobblegut (his pet crocodile). If it hits, the enraged crocodile gains a +2 status bonus to attack and damage rolls and must spend its next turn Striking the nearest creature other than Gaedren (Gaedren is immune to this forced target). This is his signature opening: he turns his own pet into a weapon, then snipes from cover.</p>"
